Document: LightOccluder2D
Path: godot/classes/class_lightoccluder2d.rst
Summary: Occludes light cast by a Light2D, requiring an OccluderPolygon2D to compute shadows.

Occludes light cast by a Light2D, casting shadows. The LightOccluder2D must be provided with an OccluderPolygon2D in order for the shadow to be computed. Note: The OccluderPolygon2D defines the shape of the occluder and is essential for shadow calculation.
