Path: godot/classes/class_lightoccluder2d.rst  
Summary: Properties and their default values for the LightOccluder2D class.  

- Property: occluder (OccluderPolygon2D): The occluder shape.  
- Property: occluder_light_mask (int): Light mask for the occluder. Default: 1.  
- Property: sdf_collision (bool): Enables SDF collision. Default: true.
